| node005 | 192.168.1.105 | root | Proxmox — control VMs |
| node006 | 192.168.1.106 | root | Proxmox — ocean VM host |
| dns01 | 192.168.1.2 | debian | BIND DNS |
| pihole | 192.168.1.9 | debian | DNS filtering |
