### SSH Examples

```bash
# Connect to ocean
ssh ocean

# Run a command remotely
ssh ocean 'systemctl status plex'

# Check disk space
ssh ocean 'df -h /data01'

# Tail service logs
ssh ocean 'journalctl -u plex --since "5 min ago" --no-pager'

# Check Docker containers
ssh ocean 'docker ps --format "table {{"{{"}}.Names{{"}}"}}\t{{"{{"}}.Status{{"}}"}}\t{{"{{"}}.Ports{{"}}"}}"'

# Restart a service
ssh ocean 'sudo systemctl restart plex'

# Check ZFS pool
ssh ocean 'zpool status data01'

# GPU status
ssh ocean 'nvidia-smi'

# Multiple commands
ssh ocean 'docker ps -q | wc -l && free -h && uptime'
```

### SSH to Proxmox Hosts

```bash
# Node management (use carefully — these are hypervisors)
ssh node005 'qm list'                    # List VMs
ssh node005 'pvesh get /nodes/node005/status'  # Node status
ssh node006 'qm list'
```

