## yq — YAML Processing

```bash
# Read a YAML value
yq -r '.service_ports.plex.port' vars/vars_service_ports.yaml

# List all service ports
yq -r '.service_ports | to_entries[] | "\(.key): \(.value.port)"' vars/vars_service_ports.yaml

# Read docker-compose service names
ssh ocean 'cat /data01/services/plex/docker-compose.yml' | yq -r '.services | keys[]'

# Check a service image version
ssh ocean 'cat /data01/services/plex/docker-compose.yml' | yq -r '.services[].image'

# Read cloudflared tunnel config
yq -r '.tunnel_ingress[] | "\(.hostname) → \(.service)"' vars/vars_cloudflared.yaml

# Combine vault view with yq
ansible-vault view vault/secrets.yaml | yq -r '.media_services | keys'
ansible-vault view vault/secrets.yaml | yq -r '.databases.mysql.root_password'
```

