## Network Diagnostics

```bash
# Test connectivity to a service
ping -c 3 192.168.1.143

# DNS lookup
dig @192.168.1.2 ocean.home
dig @192.168.1.2 +short plex.home

# Reverse DNS
dig @192.168.1.2 +short -x 192.168.1.143

# Trace network path
mtr -r -c 5 192.168.1.143

# Check if a port is open
nc -zv 192.168.1.143 32400    # Plex
nc -zv 192.168.1.143 8080     # llama.cpp
nc -zv 192.168.1.143 9090     # Prometheus

# Scan open ports on a host
nmap -sT -p- 192.168.1.143 --open

# Quick top-ports scan
nmap -sT --top-ports 100 192.168.1.143

# Check HTTP endpoint
curl -s -o /dev/null -w "%{http_code}" http://192.168.1.143:9090/-/healthy

# Whois lookup
whois terrac.com
```

