## Debugging Playbook Reference

Quick reference for common debugging tasks:

```bash
# Service won't start — check everything
ssh ocean 'systemctl status <service> && docker compose -f /data01/services/<service>/docker-compose.yml logs --tail 50'

# Container crash loop — check OOM or config
ssh ocean 'docker inspect <container> | jq ".[0].State"'
ssh ocean 'journalctl -u <service> --since "1 hour ago" --no-pager | tail -100'

# Disk space issue
ssh ocean 'df -h && du -sh /data01/services/* | sort -h | tail -20'
ssh ocean 'docker system df'

# Memory pressure
ssh ocean 'free -h && docker stats --no-stream --format "table {{"{{"}}.Name{{"}}"}}\t{{"{{"}}.MemUsage{{"}}"}}\t{{"{{"}}.MemPerc{{"}}"}}" | sort -k3 -rh | head -20'

# GPU issues
ssh ocean 'nvidia-smi && docker inspect llamacpp | jq ".[0].HostConfig.DeviceRequests"'

# Network issues
ssh ocean 'ss -tlnp | grep <port>'
curl -s http://192.168.1.143:<port>/health

# ZFS issues
ssh ocean 'zpool status data01 && zfs list -o name,used,avail,refer data01'

# Docker networking
ssh ocean 'docker network ls && docker network inspect bridge | jq ".[0].Containers"'
```
